{"tid":2210647,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣國防部推積木動畫「打爆惡龍」 展現決心抵抗中共挑釁","createTime":"2020-09-20T14:33:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T14:41:54.000Z","uid":337052,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8f4934b347e6364b8483d6bf30d7789b05c4dc5a","tid":2210647,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T14:33:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">國防部推積木動畫「打爆惡龍」 展現決心抵抗中共挑釁</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/09/20/phpQhl8LN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F09%2F20%2FphpQhl8LN.jpg&h=92f1f2e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n積木人也實行「濱海決勝、灘岸殲敵」戰術。（圖擷取自《青年日報》臉書）<br />\n<br />\n2020/09/20 22:11<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕<span class=\"red\">共軍近期頻頻出動軍機進行軍事挑釁，多次進逼為威嚇領空，國防部心理作戰大隊18日和《青年日報》合作推出一部樂高動畫，故事中以惡龍暗喻中共，最後在島上人民團結一心下成功打敗惡龍。</span><br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，這支名為「團結一心抵禦惡龍」的動畫，故事中描述積木王國有座美麗的小島，島上的人們純樸善良，過著安和樂利、自由民主的生活，但有一個壞鄰居「惡龍」一直想要破壞小島的生活，結果有天惡龍來襲，最後島上的人民團結一起，打敗惡龍，守護了美麗的家園。<br />\n<br />\n針對中共當局近期民民出動軍力擾台的行為，我國軍方在今天（20日）強調，雖然我軍「不開第一槍」，<span class=\"red\">但若中共有攻台前準備，或對我方戰機有明確攻擊跡象，可由空作部指揮官命令飛行員進行「自衛反擊權」</span>，「若國軍被攻擊，一定會反擊」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ydnews123/videos/351264259332956\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fydnews123%2Fvideos%2F351264259332956&d=eCiXx0TsV7ZnsYjNRM2Omi6Ol0HYJA13lVA%2BPgi6hPY%3D&h=ddc087d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ydnews123/videos/351264259332956</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3298031\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3298031&d=eCiXx0TsV7ZnsYjNRM2Omi6Ol0HYJA13lVA%2BPgi6hPY%3D&h=db14073d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3298031&h=bffce6c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3298031</a>"},{"pid":"5c80356ef110b198901fc27f4f6b241ae75077b3","tid":2210647,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T14:34:52.000Z","msg":"青年日報 <br />\n9月18日下午9:23  &middot; <br />\n團結一心抵禦惡龍<br />\n惡龍來襲！！！<br />\n需要全國人民上下齊心、團結在一起、發揮總體力量<br />\n一定能成功擊退惡龍，守護美麗的家園~<br />\n（國防部心理作戰大隊 製作）<br />\n#凝聚守護家園的決心<br />\n#發揮團結禦敵的力量<br />\n👇更多新聞看這邊👇<br />\n📌<a href=\"https://www.nownews.com/news/5065051\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F5065051&d=eCiXx0TsV7ZnsYjNRM2Omi6Ol0HYJA13lVA%2BPgi6hPY%3D&h=bc99aa6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nownews.com/news/5065051</a><br />\n📌<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/10930/4873129\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F10930%2F4873129&d=eCiXx0TsV7ZnsYjNRM2Omi6Ol0HYJA13lVA%2BPgi6hPY%3D&h=dd18ba86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/10930/4873129</a>"},{"pid":"42ee6284a12fae69fc8404fad693bdd0529f2685","tid":2210647,"uid":653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T14:35:04.000Z","msg":"紅色巨龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e24a1a934a6eb5e22ae44ad825f7298483290d74","tid":2210647,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42ee6284a12fae69fc8404fad693bdd0529f2685","tid":2210647,"uid":653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T14:35:04.000Z","msg":"紅色巨龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T14:41:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}